.TH "vmw_validation_bo_validate_single" 9 "vmw_validation_bo_validate_single" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
vmw_validation_bo_validate_single \- Validate a single buffer object.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" vmw_validation_bo_validate_single
.BI "(struct ttm_buffer_object *bo "  ","
.BI "bool interruptible "  ","
.BI "bool validate_as_mob "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "bo" 12
The TTM buffer object base.
.IP "interruptible" 12
Whether to perform waits interruptible if possible.
.IP "validate_as_mob" 12
Whether to validate in MOB memory.
.SH "RETURN"
Zero on success, -ERESTARTSYS if interrupted. Negative error
code on failure.
